  "text": "Theorem 2.6 ( [CITATION_1] ). There exists a unique admissible Borel structure on E φ . Furthermore, let α be an E 0 -semigroup with product system F , and suppose α is a minimal dilation of φ. Then there is a canonical product system isomorphism ψ : E φ → F .",
